description: This header file defines internal functions and prototypes for the Slap Object Wrapper (SLAP OWO) component, specifically related to setting object names and party addresses within the SLAP framework.

methods.name: SlapOwoSetObjName
methods.description: Sets the name of the object within the SLAP OWO component.

methods.name: SlapOwoSetLpcPartyAddr
methods.description: Sets the LPC party address for the SLAP OWO object.

methods.name: SlapOwoSetLpcPartyName
methods.description: Sets the LPC party name for the SLAP OWO object.
